  npcName: Veymar, Keeper of the Veil
  prompt: Talk
  lines:
  - The Veil fractures..crimson blight spills through hollow halls of flesh and iron.
  - Corruption devours the very veins of neon that once lit our world.
  - "The hordes that come are not begotten, but forged, reworked in the corruption\u2019s
    guise."
  - Cleanse the crystal when the slaughter wanes, the portal shall shape its remnants
    into power.
  dialogue: {fileID: 0}
  autoAdvanceSeconds: 4
